description:
Prototyping is a collection of helpers for MVC to assist with wireframing.

Quickly generate lorem ipsum for wireframing using the Ipsum helper and fluent api. @Html.Ipsum().h1().p().h2().p()

Easily generate placeholder images using the Placehold helper. @Html.Placehold(300, 400).
releaseNotes:
1.3
Added htmlAttributes to the table API

1.2
Added table element

1.1
Added dl > dd element

1.0
Initial release

Placeholder helper uses the http://placehold.it service and requires a network connection.
Credits to http://code.google.com/p/nlipsum/ for the NLipsum generator.
summary: Prototyping is a collection of helpers for MVC to assist with wireframing. The collection contains a helper for generating lorem ipsum, and a helper for generating image placeholders.
title: Prototyping for MVC
